Wow!

59:02.805 --> 59:05.535
Hey, Camille. Cammie.
Remember us?

59:07.744 --> 59:08.802
Should we come in?

59:08.878 --> 59:09.867
Okay.

59:09.946 --> 59:12.414
They are in their room.
Mom's going to wear a little skirt.

59:13.650 --> 59:14.742
