59:38.908 --> 59:44.175
Auf wiedersehen, goodbye

59:44.581 --> 59:47.141
Goodbye

59:47.216 --> 59:49.047
There she is.

59:50.019 --> 59:52.078
Verona, you look amazing.
Thanks.

59:52.155 --> 59:53.952
Perfect. Perfect.

59:54.023 --> 59:55.490
Hey.

59:55.925 --> 59:56.914
Good to see you.

59:56.993 --> 59:58.961
It's great to see you.
Here, watch this.

01:00:03.533 --> 01:00:07.367
